<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent Andrey Golubov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow April 21 TASS -- Great significance is being 
attached to the Panamanian Foreign Minister Jose Raul Mulino's 
forthcoming Moscow visit, which begins on April 25, in both 
Russia and that Latin American country, the Russian Foreign 
Ministry spokesman Mikhail Demurin said at a briefing today. 
