BFN 

  [Text] Vilnius, Apr 21, BNS -- Lithuanian Foreign Minister 
Povilas Gylys, currently on a Latin American trip, met with his 
Brazilian counterpart Celso Amorim in Brasilia Apr. 19. 
  The two ministers exchanged information about the internal 
situation in their countries, discussed regional problems and 
possibilities to expand bilateral cooperation, the Lithuanian 
Foreign Ministry said. Gylys presented draft agreements on 
