Brazilian parliament, the chairman of the Supreme Federal Court 
and the minister of industry, trade and tourism, Elec Alvares 
[name as received]. Gylys invited the Brazilian minister to 
visit Lithuania during his upcoming European trip. The 
ministers agreed to exchange visits of trade delegations. 
  The same day Gylys paid a visit to the Lithuanian community 
in Sao Paulo. 
  On Wednesday [20 April], the Lithuanian foreign minister was 
scheduled to visit Rio de Janeiro. 

