<H3> <TI>   State Duma Begins Moving Into New Building </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State Duma Begins Moving Into New Building </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2304143094 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1000 GMT 
23 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2304143094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In accordance with the president's edict, the 
Russian State Duma began to move into its official quarters, a 
complex of buildings in Okhotnyy Ryad in the center of Moscow. 
The Duma's first plenary session in the new building will be on 
11 May. 

</TEXT>

