  [Text] A new public organization has been established in 
Russia today, the Left-Wing Russia Party [Levaya Rossiya 
Partiya]. Steering Committee Chairman Vladimir (Burlyugov) said 
the party's main objectives were the establishment of a single 
multi-ethnic state, the renaissance of patriotism, and an 
