22 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2204164594 </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty Kazakh Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Kazakh </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Foreign minister Saudabayev today received Chen Di, 
the Chinese ambassador to Kazakhstan. They stressed that the 
mechanism of summit contacts is working efficiently. The 
forthcoming visit to Almaty by Prime Minister Li Peng testifies 
to this fact. In the opinion of both sides, this visit will 
play an important role in concrete development and 
implementations of agreements reached in October last year 
during Nazarbayev's visit to China. The signing of an agreement 
on the state border between Kazakhstan and China and other 
documents will be of great importance. 

</TEXT>

