<F P=106> [Unattributed POSTFACTUM report: "People's Assembly `Has </F>
Canceled' the Russian Federation President's Edict"] 
  [Text] Yesterday a session of the Tatarstan People's 
Assembly Presidium promulgated a statement adopted by parliament 
which rules null and void Boris Yeltsin's edict On Regulating 
Land Relations and Promoting the Agrarian Reform in Russia, 
because, according to the People's Assembly, this edict "is 
effectively tantamount to occupation and enslavement of peoples." 

