<H3> <TI>   Legal Assistance Pact Concluded With Kazakhstan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Legal Assistance Pact Concluded With Kazakhstan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS2204181894 Tallinn BNS in English 1546 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>
