<H4>    Cetin Expresses Support for Azerbaijan </H4>

<F P=102> TA2404144794 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1420 GMT 24 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA2404144794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>
