<H3> <TI>   Three Parties Want Elections Postponed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Three Parties Want Elections Postponed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2504101994 Kiev UT-1 Television Network in Ukrainian 1600 
GMT 23 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2504101994 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UT-1 Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The elections of a president and of bodies of local 
power should be postponed to the end of the year and take place 
after a new constitution has been adopted. This is included in 
statements by the Political Council of Ukraine's Green Party, 
the Democratic Party of Ukraine, and the Congress of Ukrainian 
Nationalists. 

</TEXT>

