<H3> <TI>   Platoon To Join Peacekeepers in Gorazde </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Platoon To Join Peacekeepers in Gorazde </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2504122194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1111 GMT 25 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2504122194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Mikhail Shevtsov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow April 25 TASS -- A Russian platoon will be 
sent to reinforce UN peace-keepers in the Muslim enclave of 
Gorazde in Bosnia, Russian Defence Minister Pavel Grachev 
announced at a press conference on Monday. 

</TEXT>

